From ad7584095721c1e14d810254a507c5c8573187b7 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jiaxing Hu <huhuvmb88@outlook.com>
Date: Thu, 18 Jun 2026 22:21:51 +1200
Subject: [PATCH 13/24] DEBUG: rocket: rk3576 whole-graph dispatch + engage
 probes (not for upstream)

Whole-graph PC iteration investigation: PC_TASK_STATUS (rk3576 offset 0x48)
multi-task completion poll with a 50ms cap, full CNA/CORE live register-block
dump, and per-unit-vs-broadcast OP_EN engage. Adds board-debug module params
(soft_reset, cpu_replay, double_kick, sptr_override, multitask_poll,
perjob_ppinit, wg_open, wg_intmask), all default to the working per-op path.
---
 drivers/accel/rocket/rocket_core.h |   4 +
 drivers/accel/rocket/rocket_drv.c  |  19 +-
 drivers/accel/rocket/rocket_job.c  | 314 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-
 3 files changed, 331 insertions(+), 6 deletions(-)

